description: This beautiful sun-filled first floor condominium offers an open-concept floor plan with soaring ceilings.  The spacious living room features a gas fireplace and sliders to an expansive private deck.  A chef’s kitchen with island and stainless-steel appliances, two generous bedrooms with bay windows and 2 full baths. Hardwood floors, in-unit laundry, central air, storage and private deeded outdoor space.
